metadata.name: BODIED
metadata.description:
In a world of fast fashion and TikTok trends, true individuality has become a rarity. What does it mean to stand out? What is considered original? 

Using makeup as an extension of pattern and design, it can transform clothing by bringing it past the hem line  onto to the skin, face and hair.

My body is a canvas and every inch functions to personify my artistic vision. I am my fashion and my fashion is alive.

Digital Photography by Mthr Trsa
Model, makeup and clothing by Laurel Charleston
